<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_81" id="39v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_81_r2l8">Marggraf <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_81_r2l9">Gnedıger herre . Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dy Judiſcheid hıe beẏ vns geſeſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l10">fürbraht . vvie Jn von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Johan<ex>nſen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l11">ewrs pruder wegen / etlich einträge <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . anders <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l12">ſie verſtanden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ewr durchleuhtikeit / cʒwiſchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l13"><expan>de<ex>m</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ ewrm pruder vnd Jn entſcheẏden vnd <expan>auſʒgeſproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l16">hab . Bitten vvir ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_81_r2l14">von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>furſte<ex>n</ex>lich<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l17">Judiſcheit / ewrn <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> vvillen beweıſen . vnd ſıe <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l18">durchleuhtikeit darynne <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l19">wöllet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen . Als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden des wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l20">getrawen . das <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir v̈mb ewr <expan>durch<ex>leuhtikeit</ex></expan> <expan>vvıllikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l21"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdienen / <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>Jnnocentu<ex>m</ex></expan> Anno <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l22">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Mılleſı<ex>m</ex>o</expan> cccc<hi rend="sup">o</hi> viceſimo </del> / M<hi rend="sup">o</hi> cccc<hi rend="sup">o</hi> xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_81" id="39v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Marggraf <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger herre, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dy judischeid hie bey uns
                        gesessen fürbraht, wie in von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Johan<ex>nsen</ex></expan>, ewrs pruder wegen etlich einträge
                                <expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> anders
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> sie verstanden
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ewr durchleuhtikeit czwischen
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewrm pruder und in
                        entscheyden und <expan>auszgesproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab. Bitten wir ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir <add>von
                                    <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>furste<ex>n</ex>lich<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan></add>
<expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> judischeit ewrn
                            <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> willen beweisen und sie
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit darynne
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen wöllet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen, als wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden des wol getrawen. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb ewr
                                <expan>durch<ex>leuhtikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        verdienen. <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>innocentu<ex>m</ex></expan> anno
                            <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan> m<hi rend="sup">o</hi>cccc<hi rend="sup">o</hi> xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
